## Icon Usage

### Emoji Icons
- Use universal emoji icons for compatibility
- Common icons: 🔄 (refresh), 📥 (download), 🔍 (search), ✅ (success), ❌ (error)
- Avoid Heroicon components that may not be available

### Icon Placement
- Place icons before text in buttons
- Use consistent icon sizing
- Ensure proper contrast in both themes
